<img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://opensource.com/sites/default/files/lead-images/laptop_screen_desk_work_chat_text.png" width="1040" height="584" alt="Person using a laptop" title="Person using a laptop" /><p>The usage of <a href="https://go.dev/" target="_blank">Go</a> is growing rapidly. It is now the preferred language for writing cloud-native software, container software, command-line tools, databases, and more. Go has had built-in <a href="https://pkg.go.dev/testing" target="_blank">support for testing</a> for quite some time now. It makes writing tests and running them using the Go tool relatively easy.</p>
